channel.title: Sibelius centenary
channel.description:
To commemorate the 100th anniversary of the Finnish composer Jean Sibelius' birth, this program focuses on his works.,Prepared by Finnish Broadcasting Company for U. of Michigan, WUOM (Radio station : Ann Arbor, Mich.). Observes centenary of composer Jan Sibelius' birth.
